<custodhist encodinganalog="561" id="a16">
	<head>Custodial History</head>
	<p>The Record of Milk Purchased ledgers were acquired for the University of Connecticut by Professor <persname>E.A. Perregaux</persname> in the late 1940s or early 1950s. They were stored in the Wilbur Cross Library until 1979, when they were transferred to the Historical Manuscripts and Archives Division of the University Libraries.</p>
</custodhist>

